room_title: Escape room "The Seance" by Escape Again Rooms in Houston
room_description: Your detective unit has been assigned an unusual case: JJ Buster, a reality TV star who exposes self-proclaimed oracles and fortune tellers, went missing! He was last seen two weeks ago, headed to a remote farm in Louisiana to uncover a new fraud Madam Trousseau. Leave your superstitions at the door: this will be no ordinary case.
